Serializable, Comparable<DefaultTableAttributes>
public enum DefaultTableAttributes
extends Enum<DefaultTableAttributes>

A simple enumeration whose values are used as attribute names by the default table mapper. When mapping the enum toString method will be used to generate the attribute names.

These preset attributes are all considered internal and should be prefixed with _

The _MTT_ID attribute will only be set if the table in question belongs to a tournament, in which case it will be set to the instance id of the tournament.

Author:
lars.j.nilsson
